OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome sunny spells at first but
OL,7,Fgenerally turning cloudier through the
OL,8,Fevening. Remaining largely dry and
OL,9,Fcloudy overnight with some clearer
OL,10,Fintervals, these mostly in the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA dry start with sunny
OL,13,Fspells. Any cloud gradually breaking
OL,14,Fup through the day to give largely
OL,15,Fclear skies and plenty of sunshine in
OL,16,Fthe afternoon. Very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
